# avatara.bcyr -- Benchmarks for avatara
#
# 45 benchmarks covering all traditions, sub-groups, registry, compose, history.
# Matches and exceeds Rust Criterion suite (29 benchmarks).

# Stdlib auto-included via cyrius.toml

